PHYSICAL REALITY AS PROJECTION OF CONSCIOUSNESS

The Fundamental Nature of Physical Reality

• Physical reality is a projection of consciousness
• In a sense, it is like a dream
• It isn't really "out there" around you
• It isn't really solid in the classical meaning of that word

How Physical Reality Forms

• Everything that exists in physical reality begins within consciousness as:
  - A resonance pattern
  - A template
  - A blueprint
• That blueprint, that energy pattern, is crystallized within consciousness
• It crystallizes into the format that you perceive and experience as physical reality

Physical Reality Contains Different Reflections

• Physical reality contains different kinds of reflections
• The basic ones are generally the positive and the negative
• But there is also the neutral

