THE PROTON REPRESENTS TRUE POSITIVE NATURE

The Proton as Positively Charged

• The proton is the positively charged particle
• It is more easily observed because it is the very nature of the element you're looking at itself
• It is the very identifying energy of the elements themselves

Easy to See Directly

• The proton is easy for you to see directly
• It doesn't have to hide
• It doesn't have to confuse you
• Doesn't have to fool you one way or the other
• It is just telling you what you are
• It is telling you what is
• It is showing you your nature

What You're Really Looking At

• When you're looking at an element (for example: gold or mercury), you are really looking at the PROTONS
• That's what you're looking at
• Because it is the protons that determine what the element is
• So they're easy to see

The Contrast with Electrons

• But the electrons - those sneaky little electrons:
  - Very tiny
  - Buzzing around in their little cluster cloud of probabilities
  - "I'm over here. No, I'm not. I'm over here. No, I'm not. We're here. No, I'm not. Fooled you. Again."

The Direct Correlation

• This shows you a direct correlation between:
  - The idea of the way the energy states themselves exist
  - The way that they actually crystallize down through your consciousness
  - Into the expression you call physical materiality

