• Scientists have discovered (or created for themselves to perceive) that even the so-called subatomic particles like the proton have other particles within them
• These are called QUARKS
• Those quarks generally also come in THREES
• This again shows you the trinity aspect of the existence of that energy
• Again: the duality and the neutral place in between

