DETAILED BREAKDOWN: THE ATOMIC-REALITY CORRESPONDENCE

The Neutron = The Neutral State of Being

**Physical Properties:**
• Contains both positive and negative charges
• Has layers - negative "skin" to attract proton, positive "body" to attract electron
• More massive than both proton and electron combined
• Can break down into proton and electron
• Gives structure to the atom

**Consciousness Properties:**
• The neutral state contains potential for both positive and negative experience
• More "massive" than either polarity - contains all possibilities
• The true reality from which all experiences arise
• The balance point from which you can create any preferred experience
• The actual YOU as an existence

The Electron = Negative Beliefs

**Physical Properties:**
• Negatively charged
• Exists in a probability cloud
• Never certain where it is exactly
• Very tiny, hard to pin down
• Whips around rapidly
• Only "solidifies" when measured/observed

**Consciousness Properties:**
• Represents disconnective, dissociative, segregative energy
• Fuzzy, ambiguous, hard to get a grip on
• Hides in your unconscious mind
• Uses fear and tricks to perpetuate itself
• Tells you lies about yourself
• Only becomes "solid" when you give it definition/observation
• Not really solid at all - just probabilities and potentials

The Proton = Positive Beliefs/True Nature

**Physical Properties:**
• Positively charged
• Easy to observe and identify
• Determines what the element actually is
• Stable and straightforward
• The identifying energy of elements

**Consciousness Properties:**
• Represents integrative, expansive, connective energy
• Reflects your true nature
• Easy to see directly - doesn't hide or confuse
• Shows you what you really are
• Your true powerful, self-empowered, creative, loving nature
• The truth of your being, spirit, essence, existence

